name: Asteroids Do Not Concern Me (V)
Lore: 'The personal fears of Vader''s minions do not affect his priorities.',
Text: 'Deploy on table. Asteroid Sanctuary is canceled. When you complete Rycar''s Run, place it out of play. During your control phase, opponent loses 1 Force for each Asteroid Field you control (limit 3). During your deploy phase, may deploy one Rycar''s Run or asteroid sector on table from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. (Immune to Alter.)',
